Init repo without kernels :

    $ repo init -u https://github.com/AOKP/platform_manifest.git -b jb-mr2

Init repo with kernels :

    $ repo init -u https://github.com/AOKP/platform_manifest.git -b jb-mr2 -g all,-notdefault,kernel

Init repo without devices, vendors and kernels (add them manually to local_manifests yourself)

    $ repo init -u https://github.com/AOKP/platform_manifest.git -b jb-mr2 -g all,-notdefault,-device,-vendor

Sync repo

    $ repo sync
